===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|艸|alt1=艹|早|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|t1=grass; plant}}. Originally referred to {{zh-l|*皂}}, and later borrowed for the “grass” sense, replacing {{zh-l|*艸}}.

===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*(r)tsuʔ|*r-tswa-n|t=grass}}; cognate with {{cog|bo|རྩྭ||grass}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}; STEDT).

Alternatively, it may be related to {{och-l|芻|hay}}, from {{der|zh|aav}}; compare {{cog|mnw|ချဲ||grass; weeds; hay}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

