===Etymology 1===
{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|くさ|alt=艸:uncommon}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|-}}, ultimately from {{inh|ja|jpx-pro|*kusa}}. Found in the ''{{w|Man'yōshū}}'', completed some time after 759 {{CE}}.<ref>{{R:ja:NKD Concise|草・艸}}</ref> Possibly cognate with {{cog|ko|꽃|tr=kkot|t=flower}}.

The development of the {{m|en|fake}}, {{m|en|amateur}} senses is unclear, but probably from an earlier meaning {{m|en|green}}, referring to the color of the grass.

